com.isti.traceview.common
Class Configuration

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Observable
      com.isti.traceview.common.Configuration
Direct Known Subclasses:
XYZconfiguration
public class Configuration
extends Observable

This class holds configuration data. Concrete realizations can add parameters and should define method of initialization (reading configuration file, defaults, by command line options etc)

Extends Observable interface, i.e this class can report to listeners about configuration changes

Author:
Max Kokoulin
